import axios from 'axios' import React, {useEffect, useState} from 'react' import { Baseurl } from '../baseurl' const Latest_courses = () => { const [course, setCourse] = useState([]) const path = useLocation(); useEffect(() => { let token = sessionStorage.Token if (token) { axios.get(`${Baseurl}createdcourse`, { params: { token: token } }).then((res) => { if (res.data) { setCourse(res.data) } }).catch((error) => { if (error.response.status === 500) { sessionStorage.setItem('Path', path.pathname) } }) } else { } }, []) return ( <>
